    "content": "Routing engine = Control Plane\nOSPF BGP Telenet session Daemons\nRPD\nMost important Protocol\nRouting Protocol Daemon\nWorks with all routing protocols\nInet.0\nRouting tables\nMG-D\nDCD\nChassisD\nVRRPD/ SNMPD\nPacket forwarding Engine = Forwarding Plane\nTraffic Line cards (forwarding tables) Switch fabric Junos Software architecture One daemon crashing in the Routing Engine will not crash other Daemons\n",
